AI Proxy Stack

This project provides installer and supervisor scripts for a local proxy chain.
It does not vendor third-party dependencies. The installer may install or invoke
third-party tools whose own licenses and terms apply, including but not limited
to Homebrew, pipx, Node.js/npm/npx, headroom-ai, ast-grep-cli, pxpipe-proxy,
squeezr-ai, difft, and scc.

Users are responsible for reviewing the licenses, terms, and network behavior
of the upstream tools they choose to install and run.
